奥运圣火由[[2004年夏季奥运会|2004年夏季奥运会]]马拉松铜牌得主[[万德雷·科代罗·利马|万德雷·科代罗·利马]]在马拉卡纳场内点燃<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2016/08/05/sports/olympics/ap-oly-rio-opening-ceremony-the-latest.html?_r=0 | title=The Latest: De Lima Lights the Olympic Cauldron | author=The Associated Press | newspaper=New York Times | date=2016-08-05 | accessdate=2016-08-05}}</ref>。原定将点燃火炬的[[贝利|贝利]]因健康问题未能出席典礼<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/olympics/rio-2016-pele-olympic-cauldron-flame-opening-ceremony-ill-health-football-a7174701.html | title=Rio 2016: Pele to miss Olympic opening ceremony as ill health prevents football icon from attending | first=Jack | last=de Menezes | newspaper=The Independent | date=2016-08-05 | accessdate=2016-08-05 | archive-date=2016-08-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805174153/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/olympics/rio-2016-pele-olympic-cauldron-flame-opening-ceremony-ill-health-football-a7174701.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。火炬塔采用锅的造型，彰显出组织者对阻止全球变暖的关注，排放量比之前的火炬塔要低，产出的火焰大小也比之前小。火焰由[[安东尼·豪|安东尼·豪]]设计的圆形{{le|动感雕塑|Kinetic art}}陪衬<ref name="yahoo-smallcauldron">{{cite web|title=Mystery Solved: Why Rio Olympics’ cauldron is so tiny|url=http://sports.yahoo.com/news/mystery-solved-why-rio-olympics-cauldron-is-so-tiny-034340802.html|website=Yahoo! Sports|accessdate=2016-08-06|archive-date=2016-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810062412/http://sports.yahoo.com/news/mystery-solved-why-rio-olympics-cauldron-is-so-tiny-034340802.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年4月，里约奥组委发言人马里奥·安德拉达表示，主办方原计划在开幕式过后，将奥运圣火移至靠近{{le|里约港|Port of Rio de Janeiro}}的公共场所，很可能会是[[坎德拉里亚教堂_(里约热内卢)|坎德拉里亚教堂]]，而非其中一个主要场馆。此举类似于[[2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会]]，当时主火炬为了方便市民观赏，位于[[温哥华会议中心|温哥华会议中心]]外，却在紧跟着于[[卑诗体育馆|穹顶室内体育场]]举办的开幕式本身结尾处的独立仪式中点燃。爱德华多·帕埃斯市长表达了将火炬放在离港口“心脏部位”更近处的渴望，认为这能作为奥运会遗产项目被振兴<ref name="ap-riomayor">{{cite web|title=Rio mayor wants Olympic cauldron near revitalized port area|url=http://espn.go.com/olympics/story/_/id/15425665/rio-de-janeiro-mayor-eduardo-paes-wants-olympic-cauldron-revitalized-port-area|publisher=Associated Press|accessdate=2016-07-06|archive-date=2016-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505063331/http://espn.go.com/olympics/story/_/id/15425665/rio-de-janeiro-mayor-eduardo-paes-wants-olympic-cauldron-revitalized-port-area|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://extra.globo.com/esporte/confirmado-pira-olimpica-ficara-no-porto-do-rio-19177894.html|date=2016-04-27|title=Confirmado: pira olímpica ficará no Porto do Rio|language=pt|work=Globo.com|accessdate=2016-08-04|archive-date=2016-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603121841/http://extra.globo.com/esporte/confirmado-pira-olimpica-ficara-no-porto-do-rio-19177894.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="itgbiz-cauldron">{{cite web|title=Olympic flame set to be located at city centre site during Rio 2016|url=http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1036779/olympic-flame-set-to-be-located-at-city-centre-site-during-rio-2016|website=InsideTheGames.biz|accessdate=2016-07-06|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630075549/http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1036779/olympic-flame-set-to-be-located-at-city-centre-site-during-rio-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

